remixlab.bias.branch

Class KeyboardBranch<E extends Enum<E>,A extends Action<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • remixlab.bias.branch.Branch<E>
      • remixlab.bias.branch.KeyboardBranch<E,A>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Reference action enum.
    A - Action enum sub-group.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Copyable

    public class KeyboardBranch<E extends Enum<E>,A extends Action<E>>
extends Branch<E>
    A Branch with a single keyboardProfile(), defining some KeyboardShortcut / (keyboard) action mappings. Keyboard branches may be appended only to an GenericKeyboardAgent. See GenericKeyboardAgent.appendBranch(String).

    Note that all the methods provided here are simply wrappers to the keyboardProfile(). See Profile.
